data.title: Job requirements - Job Bank
data.meta_description: Find out what is typically needed to work as a school principal in Canada. See what education, training or certification is usually required to practice this occupation. Visit Job Bank to learn more about professional licensing and other regulatory requirements in Canada.
data.text:
Do you want to work in another province or territory?

If you are already certified to work in a regulated occupation in your province or territory, it will be easier for you to have your certification recognized in another province or territory. See the Workers Mobility's website to learn more.
